  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 3rd level, an archer can choose one of the following combat maneuvers\
    \ or actions: disarm, feint, or sunder. He can perform this action with a bow\
    \ against any target within 30 feet, with a –4 penalty to his CMB. Every four\
    \ levels beyond 3rd, he may choose an additional trick shot to learn. These maneuvers\
    \ use up arrows as normal.\nAt 11th level, he may also choose from the following\
    \ combat maneuvers: bull rush, grapple, trip. A target grappled by an arrow can\
    \ break free by destroying the archer's arrow (hardness 5, hit points 1, break\
    \ DC 13) or with an Escape Artist or CMB check (against the archer's CMD –4)."
